---
<h2 class="mb-6 text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-none">
    <span class="gradient-text">About me</span>
</h2>
<p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-lg">Passionate about sports, I see physical activity as a source of well-being and personal growth. My main discipline is football, which I have practiced from an early age, allowing me to develop essential values such as respect, teamwork, and resilience.</p>
<div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full">
    <hr class="w-64 h-0.5 my-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-violet-500/50 to-transparent border-0 rounded-full">
    <div class="absolute px-4 -translate-x-1/2 left-1/2 bg-[#0a0a0f]">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-700 text-gray-300" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 18 14">
            <path d="M6 0H2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4v1a3 3 0 0 1-3 3H2a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h1a5.006 5.006 0 0 0 5-5V2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2Zm10 0h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4v1a3 3 0 0 1-3 3h-1a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h1a5.006 5.006 0 0 0 5-5V2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2Z"/>
        </svg>
    </div>
</div>
<p class="text-gray-300 font-medium mb-10 text-lg">I consider sports to be a fundamental pillar of life, not only for its health benefits but also for its ability to foster discipline, camaraderie, and strong relationships.</p>

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 justify-items-center">
    {PHOTOS.map(photo => (
        <figure class="relative max-w-sm transition-all duration-500 cursor-pointer filter grayscale hover:grayscale-0 items-center group">
            <div class="max-w-sm p-4 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-white/5 to-transparent backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-violet-500/30 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 glow-on-hover">
                <AboutItem {...photo} />
            </div>              
        </figure>
    ))}
</div>